{"tid":1116443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓團演唱會名稱現「韓國娛」3字 網友罵爆：是多想發大財？","createTime":"2019-04-20T04:08:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T06:23:54.000Z","uid":164771,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"85a74bc60f644485685dc0074d0150c0da290a64","tid":1116443,"uid":164771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:08:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpp0mRdr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpp0mRdr.jpg&h=1eb85c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將在5月19日在南港展覽館舉辦的拼盤演唱會「K-Pop Entertaining Music Festival韓國娛音樂饗宴」，主辦單位今日在臉書公佈售票資訊，不過演唱會名稱中的「韓國娛」讓許多網友及粉絲都聯想到高雄市長韓國瑜，紛紛不滿地在主辦單位臉書底下留言：「主辦是多想發大財？」<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n這場「K-Pop Entertaining Music Festival韓國娛音樂饗宴」演唱會陣容堅強，登場歌手包括少女時代隊長太妍、EXO主唱CHEN，他們的師弟團NCT DREAM也一同共襄盛舉，另外還有人氣女團MOMOLAND和男團GOLDEN CHILD，日前公布歌手名單時就讓許多粉絲十分期待，不過粉絲在期待之餘，演唱會名稱卻令人傻眼，名稱中的「韓國娛」和高雄市長韓國瑜讀音相同，當時就已經引起粉絲及網友不滿，而今日公佈售票資訊時，名稱中仍維持「韓國娛」三字不變。<br />\n<br />\n許多粉絲看到演唱會名稱後都紛紛直言：「主辦是多想發大財？」、「可以不要把演唱會跟政治勾在一起嗎，很噁心。」、「看到名字就不想買票了。」、「要去的可能會不小心變成韓粉喔～」、「名字噁到爆！」、「垃圾諧音活動名....」、「這個海報真的很廉價...」"},{"pid":"448796a685566aa80f0f2959200066efc7abfed8","tid":1116443,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf06f32e5174f45eb533beddb0c23dcbcb72f01","tid":1116443,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"同宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98b151554dde272fde66e98c7c1561683d757d6","tid":1116443,"uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:28:56.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜VS韓國娛樂圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511cd4635e16fbf47324a4d6d68a7ede3c3cbaa7","tid":1116443,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:30:44.000Z","msg":"韓國愚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b100c795745093a0f848d6497947eb37d2bcb93","tid":1116443,"uid":30743,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:31:33.000Z","msg":"Golden Child<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇LIHKG Child"},{"pid":"d72ead9da58ba7ab29d602664aed61d0861399f3","tid":1116443,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"咁的確係娛樂下你姐"},{"pid":"b233d1e5f93ed45cf1b0274321ef68a7289c29cb","tid":1116443,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T06:23:54.000Z","msg":"做乜自貶身價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />求其搵件韓仔都靚仔過佢啦<br />\n泡菜瑜應該係我見識過最醜樣嘅Daniel"}]}